---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="AI for Agencies & Consultants | Scott Armbruster" description="Scale your agency without scaling headcount. AI automation for prospect qualification, proposal generation, and client delivery.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <p class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase mb-6">
          AI for Agencies & Consultants
        </p>

        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
          Scale Output,
          <br />
          <span class="text-white">
            Not Headcount
          </span>
        </h1>

        <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-slate-200 mb-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto font-light">
          AI systems that let a 6-person agency deliver like a 20-person team
        </p>

        <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Your margins shrink every time you hire. AI automation handles prospect qualification,
          proposal drafts, research, and reporting so your senior team focuses on strategy and relationships.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold transition inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2"
          >
            Book Free Discovery Call
          </a>
          <a
            href="/calculators/quick-wins"
            class="bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold transition inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2"
          >
            Find Your Quick Wins
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Use Cases -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-slate-900/50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Where Agencies Get the Biggest Wins</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-300">
          These automations typically save 15-30 hours per week for a small agency team
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue-400 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"/>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Prospect Qualification</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
            AI chatbot on your website qualifies inbound leads, asks the right questions, and books calls with prospects that match your ideal client profile.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue-400 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Proposal Generation</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
            Feed in discovery call notes, get a polished first draft in minutes. Your team refines instead of starting from scratch every time.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue-400 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 17v-2m3 2v-4m3 4v-6m2 10H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Client Reporting</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
            Automated data pulls from Google Analytics, ad platforms, and CRM. Reports drafted and formatted before your team even opens them.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue-400 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"/>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Research & Briefs</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
            Competitive analysis, market research, and creative briefs generated from prompts your team defines once and reuses across clients.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue-400 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Email & Outreach</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
            Personalized outreach sequences that feel hand-written. AI drafts based on prospect data, your team approves and sends.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue-400 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Meeting Summaries</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
            Every client call transcribed, summarized, and turned into action items that sync to your project management tool automatically.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 border-t border-slate-800/60">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Stop Trading Hours for Dollars</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 mb-8">
        Book a free discovery call and I'll map out which automations would have the highest
        impact on your agency's margins and capacity.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold transition"
        >
          Book Discovery Call
        </a>
        <a
          href="/calculators/savings-challenge"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold transition"
        >
          Take the $1,500 Challenge
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
